Approx. 2.5 miles to I-90 via Exit 59 (Dunkirk/Fredonia)

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The property is located in proximity to downtown Dunkirk, the Lake Erie shoreline, Dunkirk Municipal Airport, and I-90. Nearby employers include Nestle Purina, Athenex, and Fieldbrook Foods.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Approximately 59 acres of vacant land available for purchase with frontage along Urban Road in Dunkirk, New York. The property is in R2 General Residential Zoning which allows for multifamily and limited commercial use.

Frontage along Urban Road provides access to utilities; adjacent to National Grid power line corridor
